VALUES(51, '3hhgd54deh', 'Plum Tomato', 'user_1/TomatoPlum.png', '<ul><li>Oval-shaped tomato with a meaty texture and fewer seeds.</li><li>Ideal for sauces and canning.</li></ul>', 2.95, 3.95, '<ul><li><strong>Shape:</strong> Oval, elongated.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Meaty, firm.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Sweet, slightly acidic.</li><li><strong>Seeds:</strong> Fewer seeds than round tomatoes.</li><li><strong>Use:</strong> Sauces, canning, paste.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '6095', '30 Days', '2025-04-03 15:25:16.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku5961', '2025-04-03 15:25:39.755', '2025-04-03 15:25:35.000', 4, 1, 1);
VALUES(52, 'df4beebh5d', 'Bamboo Shoot', 'user_1/bamboo_shoot.png', '<ul><li>Edible shoots of bamboo plants, harvested when young.</li><li>Used in various Asian cuisines for their crunchy texture and mild flavor.</li></ul>', 3.60, 6.90, '<ul><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Crunchy, crisp.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mild, slightly sweet, earthy.</li><li><strong>Forms:</strong> Fresh, canned, pickled.</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Creamy white to pale yellow.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '8775', '90 Days', '2025-04-03 15:38:08.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku9136', '2025-04-03 15:38:32.419', '2025-04-03 15:38:29.000', 4, 1, 2);
VALUES(53, 'ed45d11g12', 'Napa Cabbage', 'user_1/Napa-Cabbage.png', '<ul><li>An oblong-shaped head of light green, crinkly leaves with white veins.</li><li>Mild, slightly sweet flavor.</li><li>Commonly used in salads, stir-fries, and kimchi.</li></ul>', 1.30, 3.10, '<ul><li><strong>Shape:</strong> Oblong, cylindrical head.</li><li><strong>Leaves:</strong> Light green, crinkled, with white veins.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mild, sweet.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Crisp.</li><li><strong>Use:</strong> Raw or cooked.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '8386', '10 Days', '2025-04-03 15:43:22.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku9733', '2025-04-03 15:43:31.754', '2025-04-03 15:43:29.000', 4, 1, 3);
VALUES(54, 'cbh53c4bfd', 'Chives', 'user_1/chives.png', '<ul><li>An oblong-shaped head of light green, crinkly leaves with white veins.</li><li>Mild, slightly sweet flavor.</li><li>Commonly used in salads, stir-fries, and kimchi.</li></ul>', 0.69, 2.40, '<ul><li><strong>Shape:</strong> Oblong, cylindrical head.</li><li><strong>Leaves:</strong> Light green, crinkled, with white veins.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mild, sweet.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Crisp.</li><li><strong>Use:</strong> Raw or cooked.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '8386', '3 Days', '2025-04-03 15:54:26.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku0813', '2025-04-03 15:54:37.140', '2025-04-03 15:54:34.000', 4, 1, 4);
VALUES(55, 'c25f3h42dh', 'Unseasoned Rice Vinegar', 'user_1/unseasoned.png', '<ul><li>Unseasoned rice vinegar is a mild vinegar made from fermented rice. &nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>It has a delicate, slightly sweet flavor compared to other vinegars.</li><li>It does not contain added sugar or salt.</li></ul>', 4.00, 6.00, '<ul><li><strong>Base:</strong> Fermented rice. &nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mildly acidic, slightly sweet.</li><li><strong>Acidity:</strong> Typically around 4-5%.</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear to pale yellow.</li><li><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Rice vinegar (diluted with water in some cases).</li></ul>', 'Organic', '9791', '100 Days', '2025-04-05 00:02:42.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku4160', '2025-04-05 00:02:58.577', '2025-04-05 00:02:56.000', 1, 1, 2);
VALUES(56, '5e54f3cbf1', 'Ground Black Pepper', 'user_1/ground_black_pepper.png', '<ul><li>Spice made from ground, dried black peppercorns.</li><li>Pungent, warm, slightly spicy flavor.</li></ul>', 3.00, 3.70, '<ul><li><strong>Form:</strong> Fine to coarse powder.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Pungent, warm, slightly earthy.</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Black.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '7787', '100 Days', '2025-04-05 00:06:59.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku9976', '2025-04-05 00:07:26.222', '2025-04-05 00:07:23.000', 1, 1, 3);
VALUES(57, 'daahegc125', 'Pork Chops', 'user_1/pork_chops.png', '<ul><li>Individual cuts of pork, typically taken from the loin.</li><li>Can be bone-in or boneless.</li><li>Versatile and widely cooked.</li></ul>', 6.66, 9.98, '<ul><li><strong>Cut:</strong> Loin (most common).</li><li><strong>Bone:</strong> Bone-in or boneless.</li><li><strong>Thickness:</strong> Varies.</li><li><strong>Fat Content:</strong> Varies by cut.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mild, takes on seasonings well.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '576', '1 Days', '2025-04-05 00:10:11.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku7239', '2025-04-05 00:10:23.771', '2025-04-05 00:10:21.000', 2, 1, 4);
VALUES(58, 'c5edcf2532', 'Kosher Salt', 'user_1/Kosher_salt.png', '<ul><li>Coarse-grained salt, typically without iodine or other additives.</li><li>Used in the Jewish practice of kashering meat (drawing out blood).</li><li>Popular among chefs for its ease of handling and pure flavor.</li></ul>', 4.80, 8.00, '<ul><li><strong>Form:</strong> Coarse crystals or flakes.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Purely salty, often perceived as cleaner than iodized table salt.</li><li><strong>Additives:</strong> Usually none (some may have anti-caking agents).</li><li><strong>Crystal Shape:</strong> Flaky (Morton) or pyramidal (Diamond Crystal).</li></ul>', 'Organic', '776', '60 Days', '2025-04-05 00:12:52.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku1356', '2025-04-05 00:13:07.686', '2025-04-05 00:13:04.000', 1, 1, 5);
VALUES(59, 'adb5fbbefd', 'Seasoned Rice Vinegar', 'user_1/seasoned_rice_vinegar.png', '<ul><li>Rice vinegar with added sugar and salt.</li><li>Sweeter and less acidic than unseasoned rice vinegar.</li><li>Commonly used for sushi rice and salad dressings</li></ul>', 2.60, 5.10, '<ul><li><strong>Base:</strong> Rice vinegar.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mildly acidic, distinctly sweet and salty.</li><li><strong>Acidity:</strong> Typically around 4-4.5%.</li><li><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Rice vinegar, sugar, salt (may contain other flavorings). &nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear to pale yellow.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '5975', '100 Days', '2025-04-05 00:18:13.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku6554', '2025-04-05 00:18:27.459', '2025-04-05 00:18:24.000', 1, 1, 6);
VALUES(60, 'g2egdh2g3b', 'Asian Fish', 'user_1/Asian_fish.png', '<p>Fresh fish, sourced from local waters or aquaculture farms, is a staple in Vietnamese cuisine. Often displayed whole or cut into portions at markets and supermarkets, these fish offer a delicate and flavorful protein. Their taste and texture vary depending on the species, but they are generally prized for their freshness and versatility in a wide range of traditional dishes.</p>', 7.80, 10.00, '<ul><li><strong>Habitat:</strong> Freshwater or saltwater.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Ranges from mild to strong, can be oily or lean.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Flaky, firm, delicate.</li><li><strong>Appearance:</strong> Varies greatly in shape, size, and color.</li><li><strong>Preparation:</strong> Suitable for steaming, frying, grilling, soups, stews, etc.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '9889', '3 Days', '2025-04-05 00:23:26.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku7236', '2025-04-05 00:23:50.660', '2025-04-05 00:23:47.000', 2, 1, 1);
VALUES(61, 'chce1g3ege', 'Liverwurst', 'user_1/liverwurst.png', '<ul><li>Smooth, spreadable sausage made mainly from liver (usually pork or beef).</li><li>Rich, savory flavor with spices.</li></ul>', 3.60, 6.90, '<ul><li><strong>Main Ingredient:</strong> Liver.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Smooth, spreadable.</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Rich, savory, spiced.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '1928', '30 Days', '2025-04-05 00:27:06.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku5786', '2025-04-05 00:28:05.243', '2025-04-05 00:27:54.000', 2, 1, 2);
VALUES(62, '2c4c2deda5', 'Lettuce', 'user_1/lettuce.png', '<p>Lettuce is a leafy vegetable, typically eaten raw in salads and sandwiches. It comes in various types with different leaf shapes, colors (green to red), and textures (crisp to soft).</p>', 0.60, 0.99, '<ul><li><strong>Types:</strong> Common types include Romaine, Iceberg, Butterhead, and loose-leaf varieties (Red Leaf, Green Leaf).</li><li><strong>Flavor:</strong> Mild, slightly sweet to sometimes slightly bitter, depending on the type.</li><li><strong>Texture:</strong> Ranges from crisp (Iceberg, Romaine) to tender (Butterhead, some loose-leaf).</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Primarily shades of green and red.</li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> Refrigerate to maintain freshness.</li></ul>', 'Organic', '4374', '2 Days', '2025-04-05 00:30:44.000', 'published', true, true, true, false, 'sku2310', '2025-04-05 00:31:00.695', '2025-04-05 00:30:57.000', 4, 1, 3);




